		WeSave is committed to revolutionizing group savings by providing a secure,
		transparent, and automated platform for communities to collectively save
		and grow wealth. Inspired by traditional savings practices like Ajo and
		Esusu, we enable users to build trusted savings circles, set financial
		goals, and benefit from structured contributions that drive economic
		empowerment.
	</p>
</div>

<div class="info-section">
	<h6>Our Vision</h6>
